race.comment: CUBAN EIGHT (6) sizzled around 380m in 21.76 when winning a Free For All at this track last start. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. JIMMY ROO (1) boasts a strong record this journey with 33 wins and 21 minors from 65 tries. Missed the frame latest (23.09) when eighth over 380m at this track in a Free For All. Suited here and expected to run well. JUDI STARLINE (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 380m behind CUBAN EIGHT (22.55) in a Free For All. Placed at her previous run. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Should play a prominent role. PIKA WAVE (7) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.
